{"tid":1288294,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)motherfucker 保鏢救殺手 邊個又殺我隻狗1-2","createTime":"2019-07-05T14:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T21:15:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f33382392cc7913a6f679618c19f67ed66f95f29","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=c22852e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=54171f78\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=392c04e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/2aeaf6/f/800x0/http://www.btbtt.co/upload/attach/004/892/61685c75c7f67470de4310ffc1f1fe3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F2aeaf6%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.btbtt.co%2Fupload%2Fattach%2F004%2F892%2F61685c75c7f67470de4310ffc1f1fe3e.jpg&h=5c7f693f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/67/The_Hitman's_Bodyguard_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F67%2FThe_Hitman%27s_Bodyguard_poster.jpg&h=688e0826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傑西&middot;厄舍加盟[殺戮戰警]續作[夏福特之子](Son of Shaft，暫譯)，塞繆爾&middot;傑克遜同時回歸。本片由蒂姆&middot;斯托瑞([佐州自救兄弟])執導，肯尼亞&middot;巴里斯編劇。厄舍扮演傑克遜的兒子，他同時也是一名聯邦調查局工作人員，更是網絡專家<br />\n<br />\n2.保鑣同殺手是多年宿敵，但同樣賤格唔收口，初則你串我我串番你，繼而有你冇我！但係既然坐埋同一條船，唔想攬炒，只好一邊互X一邊盡快完成任務。邊個估到，一段世上最矛盾又最曖昧的關係，由此展開&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西..<br />\n<br />\n4.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=27f91fed\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=91c06550\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3070920944854fb078a9410d1684b8068aa0d601","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172938a5a1a3af329b27bb1b5dcc3baef2921846","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53d1813c9aea7e92fb14bc13459801912f2c204","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59286d6cc6fbbf2673851cda6305625243dd5989","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f0eecfd754a8d6631bd36f1b45fb00754816e1","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd91a02c7ee8ab001d0198c9ef004c40248b04e2","tid":1288294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026876557ce42